    "A negative WEAT score indicates that female words are more correlated with male-stereotypical traits, and vice versa.",
    "To target words that potentially demonstrate gender stereotypes, we identify and highlight words that could be categorized within the nine lexicon categories in Table 2, and run WEAT test on these identified words.",
